<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA3">
<l>paricu naṟumalarāṟ pāṟkaṭalāṉ pātam</l>
<l>purivār pukappeṟuvar pōlām purivārkaḷ</l>
<l>tollamarar kēḷvit tulaṅkoḷicēr tōṟṟattu</l>
<l>nallamarar kōmāṉ ṉakar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who worship the feet of the one from the milk ocean</l>
<l>with excellent  fragrant blossoms, it seems as if  they will get to enter</l>
<l>the city of the king of good immortals, with an appearance of light</l>
<l>that shines with the aural teaching of the ancient immortals  who worship [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
